Package com.seailz.discordjv.model.emoji.sticker

Record Class Sticker

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.seailz.discordjv.model.emoji.sticker.Sticker
Record Components:
id - The id of the sticker
packId - The id of the pack the sticker is from
name - The name of the sticker
description - The description of the sticker
tags - The tags for the sticker
type - The StickerType of the sticker
format - The StickerFormat of the sticker
available - Whether or not the sticker is available
guildId - The id of the guild that owns this sticker
user - The user that uploaded the guild sticker
sortValue - The standard sticker's sort order within its pack
All Implemented Interfaces:
Compilerable
